{
  "name": "[EXAMPLE] 04 - Hiring Campaign (Multi-Layer)",
  "description": "Full hiring campaign with Layer 1 (job post), Layer 2 (commercial/image/video), Layer 3 (services), Layer 4 (publish). Agentic Prompt: prompthiringad1. Agent: Randy (9201). Cycles: 15-25.",
